[Student "S"]
{It is possible your side can make 3NT on this deal. You have 9 points, invitational strength, and your \D stopper is excellent.

However you should look for an even bigger reward by doubling. North is in serious trouble, and when the opponents make a mistake you should punish them.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "E:KJ93.AQ87.95.AQ7 A52.9532.KQJ632. QT84.K6.AT7.KT83 76.JT4.84.J96542"]
